{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "smartcity-overview",
  "title": "Smart City Overview",
  "tags": ["smartcity"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 2,
  "refresh": "15s",
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Active Vehicles",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "mappings": [{ "options": { "0": { "text": "5" } }, "type": "value" }]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "vector(5)",
          "legendFormat": "Vehicles",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Spark Master — Workers Online",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 4, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "green", "value": 3 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "spark_master_aliveWorkers",
          "legendFormat": "Workers",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Spark — Apps Running",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 8, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "green", "value": 2 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "spark_master_apps",
          "legendFormat": "Running Apps",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Spark — Cores Used / Total",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "min": 0,
          "max": 6,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 4 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 6 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "spark_master_coresUsed",
          "legendFormat": "Cores Used",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Spark — Memory Used (MiB)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 16, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 3000 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 5000 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "decmbytes"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "spark_master_memoryUsed / 1024 / 1024",
          "legendFormat": "Memory MiB",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Prometheus — Self Scrape Duration",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 20, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 5 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "s",
          "mappings": []
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "scrape_duration_seconds{job=\"prometheus\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Scrape time",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Spark — Cores Used Over Time",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 15 }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "spark_master_coresUsed",
          "legendFormat": "Cores Used",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "spark_master_cores",
          "legendFormat": "Cores Total",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "Spark — Running Applications Over Time",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 15 }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "spark_master_apps",
          "legendFormat": "Running Apps",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "spark_master_waitingApps",
          "legendFormat": "Waiting Apps",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "Pipeline Architecture",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Smart City Data Pipeline — Cairo & New Administrative Capital, Egypt\n\n### Real-Time Path\n`Vehicle Simulator (5 cars)` → `Kafka (vehicle-telemetry, 3 partitions)` → `Spark Alert Detector` → `Kafka alerts topic` *(sub-second latency)*\n\n### Batch Path  \n`Kafka` → `Spark Bronze Writer (30s micro-batch)` → `S3 Bronze (raw Parquet, 7d retention)`  \n→ `Spark Silver Cleaner (60s trigger)` → `S3 Silver (cleaned + validated, 30d retention)`  \n→ `Airflow @hourly` → `Spark Gold Aggregator (batch)` → `S3 Gold (KPIs, 1yr retention)`  \n→ `Snowflake DWH` → `dbt transformations` → `Grafana Dashboards`\n\n### Kafka Topics\n`vehicle-telemetry` (3p) · `weather-data` (1p) · `traffic-events` (2p) · `road-events` (1p) · `alerts` (1p)\n\n### Stack\nPython 3.11 · Kafka 7.5.0 · Spark 3.5.3 · AWS S3 · Airflow 2.8.1 · Snowflake · dbt Core · Grafana 10.2.2 · Prometheus"
      }
    }
  ],
  "templating": { "list": [] },
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "links": []
}